OL,3,CCharles arrives in Bermuda after
OL,4,Csuccessful US state visit
OL,6,FThe King has arrived in Bermuda for a
OL,7,Fthree-day royal trip on the back of a
OL,8,Fmemorable state visit to America.
OL,10,FCharles and Camilla were waved off
OL,11,Ffrom Washington by President Donald
OL,12,FTrump and a few hours later, the King
OL,13,Ftouched down in Bermuda for a solo
OL,14,Ftour.
OL,16,FHe landed on Thursday evening after Mr
OL,17,FTrump announced he would remove
OL,18,Ftariffs from Scottish whisky,
OL,19,Fprompting Buckingham Palace to say the
OL,20,FKing would be toasting the President
OL,21,Fwith a dram.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
