PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777619131
OL,3,CCharles arrives in Bermuda after
OL,4,Csuccessful US state visit
OL,6,FMr Trump said it was Charles and
OL,7,FCamilla's intervention that prompted
OL,8,Fthe important decision.
OL,10,FMark Kent, chief executive of the
OL,11,FScottish Distillers Association, said
OL,12,F"distillers can breathe a little
OL,13,Feasier" following the move.
OL,15,FThe major development will vindicate
OL,16,FDowning Street's decision to send the
OL,17,FKing on the trip, viewed by some as
OL,18,Fhighly risky, to repair the UK-US
OL,19,Fspecial relationship.
