OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1777619131
OL,3,CCharles arrives in Bermuda after
OL,4,Csuccessful US state visit
OL,6,FThe King and Queen thanked the US for
OL,7,Fthe welcome they received in a message
OL,8,Fon X.
OL,10,FThe couple said: "We leave a piece of
OL,11,Four heart behind and take a little of
OL,12,Fyours back home with us.
OL,14,F"Until the next time... God Bless
OL,15,FAmerica."
OL,17,FArriving at LF Wade International
OL,18,FAirport at dusk, the UK Government's
OL,19,FVIP Airbus plane flew the Royal
OL,20,FStandard and Bermuda flag from the
OL,21,Fcockpit window.
OL,26,@rD@ROUvD@AOUwD@IO]
