OL,3,CCharles arrives in Bermuda after
OL,4,Csuccessful US state visit
OL,6,FCharles was greeted by the Governor of
OL,7,FBermuda Andrew Murdoch and the Premier
OL,8,Fof Bermuda David Burt and his wife
OL,9,FKristin, with a small guard of honour
OL,10,Fformed by the Royal Bermuda Regiment
OL,11,Fstanding to attention nearby.
OL,13,FThe formalities were low-key, as the
OL,14,FKing will receive a ceremonial welcome
OL,15,Fof pomp and pageantry featuring a 21-
OL,16,Fgun salute on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
