OL,3,CCharles arrives in Bermuda after
OL,4,Csuccessful US state visit
OL,6,FWhen he reached the end of the red
OL,7,Fcarpet, the King pointed at the
OL,8,Ftravelling UK media and said "you made
OL,9,Fit" before climbing into his waiting
OL,10,Fcar.
